                    While  various  Unix  utilities have been de-
                    signed to take advantage of  the  CRT  screen
                    (rather than line-oriented systems) electron-
                    ic mail systems haven't ``caught the  wave''.
                    This  document  presents _E_l_m, a sophisticated
                    full-screen mail system for interactive  use.
                    _E_l_m  offers  all  the  features of _/_b_i_n_/_m_a_i_l,
                    _B_e_r_k_e_l_e_y _M_a_i_l, _u_u_m_a_i_l,  _N_M_a_i_l  and  the  AT&T
                    Mail family of Unix mailers (namely _P_M_X_/_T_E_R_M)
                    in a unified and intuitive fashion.


