          Consequently, after becoming more and more disenchanted with  the
          existing electronic mail facilities (_b_i_n_m_a_i_l and _B_e_r_k_e_l_e_y _M_a_i_l) I
          decided to undertake creating my own system.  Once the  ball  was
          rolling it became quite difficult not to keep enhancing it, espe-
          cially as I became more and more familiar with various  different
          mail  systems, but the result, I hope, is a solid, unified inter-
          face to electronic mail suitable for almost any environment.

          One thing that sets TThhee EEllmm MMaaiill SSyysstteemm off from  other  packages
          is  that it comes with an extensive documentation set, including;
